text.tspan: A collaborative workplace with private spaces integrated with nature
Proof of concept for Datalayer, Inc.
at Avenue de la princesse, 5 - 7322 Ville-Pommeroeul
The requirements are important, not the effective schema
Instead of adding a work area for online workers in their existing private home,
a Well Office place allows online workers to benefit from a motivating and relaxing
journey. This is especially well suited for nomad workers connected with peers
all around the globe. The private spaces mix with the work areas, removing the
need to commute after the working day.
